### Restaurant Settings & Password Management APIs
@baseUrl = http://localhost:3000

### ============================================
### RESTAURANT SETTINGS APIs
### ============================================

### 1. Get Restaurant Settings
GET {{baseUrl}}/restaurant-settings
Content-Type: application/json

### 2. Update Restaurant Settings
PUT {{baseUrl}}/restaurant-settings
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "restaurantName": "Nhà Hàng Món Ngon",
  "address": "123 Đường ABC, Quận 1, TP.HCM",
  "phoneNumber": "0901234567",
  "email": "contact@nhahang.com",
  "openingTime": "09:00",
  "closingTime": "23:00",
  "description": "Nhà hàng chuyên các món ăn Việt Nam truyền thống",
  "logo": "/images/logo.png",
  "taxRate": 10,
  "serviceCharge": 5,
  "currency": "VND",
  "timezone": "Asia/Ho_Chi_Minh"
}

### 3. Update Partial Settings (chỉ cập nhật một số trường)
PUT {{baseUrl}}/restaurant-settings
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "restaurantName": "Nhà Hàng ABC",
  "openingTime": "10:00",
  "closingTime": "22:00"
}

### ============================================
### PASSWORD MANAGEMENT APIs
### ============================================

### 4. Change Password (yêu cầu mật khẩu cũ)
POST {{baseUrl}}/restaurant-settings/change-password
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "userId": "676889e4a5e1234567890abc",
  "oldPassword": "admin123",
  "newPassword": "newpassword123"
}

### 5. Admin Reset Password (không cần mật khẩu cũ)
POST {{baseUrl}}/restaurant-settings/admin-reset-password
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "userId": "676889e4a5e1234567890abc",
  "newPassword": "resetpassword123"
}

